{"tid":997560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨上水反水貨遊行 陳淨心踩場 化妝品店即落閘 !","createTime":"2019-01-27T09:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T09:18:02.000Z","uid":49388,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"82b3ab0f3a71e9d6ad0823a60f915113bcc98adb","tid":997560,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190127/59191140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59191140&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=008791b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190127%2F59191140&h=0e3bc2a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190127/59191140</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨於上水發起反水貨遊行，抗議水貨客擾亂上水居民生活，要求政府將自由行「一周一行」改為「一年八行」，民主黨稱約200人參與。遊行期間，愛港行動現身「踩場」，派發國旗及以咪高峰「打對台」。<br />\n<br />\n遊行由水貨客問題嚴重的新康街起步，途經數個水貨黑點後折返。民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，水貨客問題向來擾亂上水居民生活，造成阻街及衞生問題，臨近農曆新年問題更嚴重。他指曾多次向政府要求打擊水貨活動但不果，北區區民忍無可忍，故發起遊行。他要求政府收緊自由行旅客來港次數，由「一周一行」改為「一年八行」，指認為能滿足正常旅客來港旅遊的需要。<br />\n<br />\n遊行起步前，新康街部份化妝品店舖迅速拉閘避風頭。愛港行動召集人陳淨心帶同6人現身遊行起步點，高舉「歡迎內地同胞來港辦年貨」紙牌及高叫口號，並向在場人士派發國旗。民主黨見狀立即反擊，在警員分隔下雙方用咪高峰「打對台」。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷要求警方按不反對通知書，確保遊行不受攻擊，陳淨心就一直行於民主黨遊行隊伍前方約20米位置。對於陳淨心有否為其集會申請不反對通知書，她辯稱其團隊只有6人，故無需申請，「（其他人）路人嚟㗎，唔識㗎」。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548572148_7873.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548572148_7873.jpg&h=37559f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨今日於上水發起反水貨遊行，指水貨客造成阻街及衞生問題，一直困擾上水居民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548574903_ac54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548574903_ac54.jpg&h=a0e441ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方將愛港行動人士與參與遊行人士分隔，林卓廷要求警方確保遊行不受攻擊。王子俊攝 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548574911_f2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548574911_f2d4.jpg&h=4773b812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨林卓廷建議將自由行「一周一行」變為「一年八行」。王子俊攝"},{"pid":"83a9f0e5113e653ed34ff2d05f49c47618957495","tid":997560,"uid":29702,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:22:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"790d524fab3f8e3b51ef902f26e39a1a1002d97a","tid":997560,"uid":168797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"6552ec21b4bb5940192937486b36eefc1c172b7b","tid":997560,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"嘩好耐無見 wor 潮州妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd945610bbaa48779b8c7bc4ba3668dfa60df0d","tid":997560,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"民主黨係咪訓左冇睇?<br />\n<br />\n而家先發現有水貨狗"},{"pid":"8e884ee8a71a6b685fcb0db41a18b6d3f3679f04","tid":997560,"uid":32706,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ddd945610bbaa48779b8c7bc4ba3668dfa60df0d","tid":997560,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"民主黨係咪訓左冇睇?<br />\n<br />\n而家先發現有水貨狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"選舉年先出嚟做show"},{"pid":"49e34fc4e8ff63adc31ca7660abffcdea78a50a4","tid":997560,"uid":38666,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"泛民譴責反水貨客示威。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨何俊仁</span>表示，示威衝擊的場面<span style=\"color: red;\">令人痛心</span>，完全<span style=\"color: red;\">超越示威的界線</span>。何俊仁期望，年青人反思這種手段，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使成功趕走水貨客，亦令全港受到傷害</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a h